# Build artifacts that confuse fresh container builds.
#
# The tsbuildinfo files are the critical exclude here: with `incremental:
# true` in tsconfig.base.json, leaving stale ones in the docker build
# context makes tsc decide "nothing changed" and silently skip emit,
# which then breaks downstream packages that import from `./dist`. Symptom
# is `Cannot find module '@sendmast/clickhouse'` even though the package
# clearly exists on disk.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/.cache

# VCS / scratch — none of this needs to be in the image.
.git
.gitignore
*.log

# Local-only files that shouldn't end up baked into a prod image.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
密钥*
edm需求文档.docx
